54
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:20,639
delusive opinions promulgating across the world.

55
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:31,840
I consider these ideas to be unhealthy because when they are implemented in law

56
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:36,559
they achieve a sort of prison.

57
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:47,519
