62
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:47,600
they need industrial output, armaments, shipping industries, steel industries;

63
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:54,159
they need to do more than retail;

64
00:11:58,399 --> 00:12:01,600
they need to do more than provide banking services;

65
00:12:06,559 --> 00:12:10,000
they need to do more than provide hotels by the seaside.

66
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:27,279
I believe it can be achievable but not without addressing concepts such as land utilisation

67
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:39,439
or land ownership because land can't be moved: land is the surface of a sphere.

68
00:12:44,799 --> 00:12:51,360
There's only so much of it that can go around and then its price increases indefinitely

69
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:55,839
as population and demand for it rises.

70
00:12:58,240 --> 00:13:04,720
Addressing these concepts is an ecological challenge.

71
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:15,759
