86
00:15:13,279 --> 00:15:22,399
A prophet is a kind of inspired teacher who sees further than somebody else.

87
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:34,399
I believe that the message of the Quran is not to copy Mohammed;

88
00:15:36,399 --> 00:15:38,399
it is not to dress like him;

89
00:15:38,959 --> 00:15:40,399
it is not to emulate him:

90
00:15:46,079 --> 00:15:56,159
but to understand the inspired messages that are written within the canon of the Islamic faith,

91
00:15:57,039 --> 00:16:06,559
